<doc id="1276896" wikidata="Q2851201" url="?curid=1276896" title="Golden Earring (album)">
<text>Golden Earring is the sixth album by Dutch rock band Golden Earring, released in 1970. Fans may refer to it as the &quot;Wall of Dolls&quot; due to the cover artwork. This is the first Golden Earring album with drummer Cesar Zuiderwijk as a member. 

==Track listing==
All songs written by Kooymans except where noted.

